This project is a macOS app for AI chat with agentic capabilities. It uses Swift and a simple build system (`build.sh`). The UI is in the code, there are no XIBs. The app is currently in active development, so no backwards compatibility is required if we're changing something.

The documentation for some of the libraries that we are using is located in `lib-docs`.

Modern UI stuff could be used since we're targeting macOS 15 or higher. Feel free to do research using one-liners with `swift -e` if needed.

Use `build.sh` to build the project and check for possible compilation errors (it's a wrapper around `swift build` that does everything to make a proper app bundle).

Don't overthink. Ask if something is unclear. If encountered a difficult problem first explain it and ask advice from the user.